name: Shingles and Clouds
description:
I paint seascapes that evoke human emotions. In this painting you can see a split between the turmoil in the clouds in the sky and the calm clear water gently lapping the shingles. 

We can exist in a space of calm while there is turmoil going on around us. It's not easy but it is possible. Human emotions are complex, in this painting  I am referencing nature as a visual aid to understanding our emotions.
